{"tid":776374,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"一次中學聚會，竟然俾班asso/ive笑我呢個degree...","createTime":"2018-08-12T04:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T06:01:29.000Z","uid":71508,"like":62,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"afeb74f3a5ce6eb52b8d2afe7f1b2ed548f72ae8","tid":776374,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:28:55.000Z","msg":"一次中學聚會，竟然俾班ASSO/IVE笑我呢個Degree <br />\n<br />\n由於我出身於一間垃圾band 3 中學，身邊冇乜邊幾個唔係冇腦。全校入到u既，五隻手指都數得哂，而自己係其中一個岩岩好夠分入u既冇腦。而當時所謂全校最top果幾位刷鞋仔/女，而家全部入哂asso/ive/恆大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾星期前，成班中學同學搞左次打邊爐聚會，我帶著全場唯一一個大學生既身份出席，入場時心情格外興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，成個人充滿自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。聚會去到一半，成晚話題大多數都係圍繞著我同我既U life，多數問我「有冇玩ocamp?」、「有冇住hall?」、「ocamp有冇玩淫game?」等等。 <br />\n<br />\n直到有位同學提出左GPA三隻字，由於我讀果科出哂名難拎高GPA，唔係NDS都好少有3.0。但係我自問成績都算係department入面既中等排名。我就答「2點幾啦，你地呢?」。果班ive 同asso即時表現一個好驚訝既表情，然後笑住講「下! 乜咁低既! 我都有3點幾喎!」一個二個對住自己既gpa打哂丁。我果時即刻笑而不語，心入邊諗你班ive /asso 俾幾萬買個垃圾學位，學校仲唔俾個高gpa你地，等你地自我感覺良好，繼續讀埋果幾年，一人交返十零廿萬學費咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢句心入邊既說話我冇講到出黎，因為我驚會hurt到真心想讀書學習既同學，但係咁樣俾d 刷鞋仔以為自己好勁，有點覺得好唔抵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d5bfea7fba3c12654dce7487fc6913eb04f9a0","tid":776374,"uid":110858,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:30:51.000Z","msg":"遲啲你成班frd齊齊後門入三大笑鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4922c767a3000b824fe8bef6ed68effaafd34d89","tid":776374,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:32:34.000Z","msg":"讀唔成書咪走後門囉"},{"pid":"17b6cf72dd9a5db4b9667e04f5c8265a085fae23","tid":776374,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"a3d5bfea7fba3c12654dce7487fc6913eb04f9a0","tid":776374,"uid":110858,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:30:51.000Z","msg":"遲啲你成班frd齊齊後門入三大笑鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:35:02.000Z","msg":"冇可能"},{"pid":"9040cfaca937fe8347c224fdfa1d8583e3963058","tid":776374,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4922c767a3000b824fe8bef6ed68effaafd34d89","tid":776374,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:32:34.000Z","msg":"讀唔成書咪走後門囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:36:01.000Z","msg":"讀得成書先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8cb06cf067e46d9bd76d547e485db3902531b4","tid":776374,"uid":199871,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:38:59.000Z","msg":"佢地BECAME ANOTHER PERSON了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48fae02a74ffdfdc00e5949cd41873e56c159df4","tid":776374,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:28:00.000Z","msg":"2/10<br />\n再接再厲"},{"pid":"3f666e46f056f8a0c58d1da0d1c0c1eeea92868a","tid":776374,"uid":71579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:35:18.000Z","msg":"做咩依排係咁出膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429ead44e11aaffc0605e126fe4b1fba1bf1812e","tid":776374,"uid":198998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:49:26.000Z","msg":"今次作得幾好唔錯<br />\n5/10"},{"pid":"8418d1